<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3567286>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–12. Adults of Ectoedemia ortiva. 9. Male (genitalia slide no. SY351). 10. Male (Genitalia slide No. SY568). 11. Hindwing. 12. Underside of male. Scale bars: 2.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3567286/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3567290>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19–23. Male genitalia of Ectoedemia ortiva. 19, 20. Genital capsule with phallus removed (Genitalia slide No. SY351). 21. Phallus. 22. Cornuti. 23. Pseuduncus and gnathos (Genitalia slide No. SY568). Scale bars: 100 μm (19–22), 50 μm (23)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3567290/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3567306>
    dc:description "FIGURES 58–63. Japanese distribution maps of Japanese species of the Ectoedmeia suberis and angulifasciella groups. 58. E. chasanella. 59. E. ortiva. 60. E. pilosae. 61. E. picturata. 62. E. occultellla. 63. E. jacutica." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3567306/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

